title: Article One Discography 2006-2010 (5 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
ARTICLE ONE DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 5 releases...

 * 2006 - Article One
 * 2008 - Colors And Sounds
 * 2008 - The Pharmacy EP
 * 2010 - Clarity
 * 2010 - The One I'm Fighting For EP

Article One is a Canadian Christian rock band from London, Ontario. The band's lineup features Nathan Piche (vocals, guitars, keyboards), Matt Piche (violin, vocals), Dave DeSmit (drums, vocals), and Nolan Verner (bass guitar).

Thankful In Him,
TorrentTracts - November 2013
